===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|束|八|t1=tie|t2=division, individually|ls=ic}}. Its original meaning is "to pick, to select, to choose", later written as {{l|zh|揀|tr=-}}. Perhaps, the two points/marks inside the pictogram of the tied bag (later stylized as {{lang|zh|八}}) mark and emphasize the content of a bag and/or the extraction of its content. See also {{l|zh|東//|tr=-}}, {{l|zh|熏//|tr=-}}, and {{l|zh|鹵//|tr=-}}.

